1290
01:36:33.746 --> 01:36:36.040
dan aku akan kembali ke dunia nyata.

1291
01:36:38.709 --> 01:36:42.296
Tapi kalian selalu nyata bagiku.
Kalian semua.

1292
01:36:52.848 --> 01:36:53.766
Gootrude...

1293
01:36:57.228 --> 01:37:00.064
